sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Procter & Gamble ( PG ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 0.2%.
Year to date, Procter & Gamble registers a 10.3% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Goldman Sachs ( GS ), trading down 1.0%.
Goldman Sachs is showing a gain of 7.2% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ), trading down 0.9%, and Boeing ( BA ), trading up 0.2% on the day.
